â€¢	Right-click the Telnet rule â†’ Delete.
7. Document steps
â€¢	Used GUI: wf.msc â†’ Inbound Rule â†’ New Rule
â€¢	Blocked 23, allowed 22, tested, then removed rule.
8. Summary
Windows Firewall filters traffic by applying inbound/outbound rules. Block rules drop traffic, while allow rules permit it.
